title: 17 Matroska Covers by CK - Release 1
description:
This is a collection of covers which I created to be eco-friendly. (less ink)

I want to make these covers freely available to all Matroska downloaders.


Primary Objective:
I have dedicated this work to the Matroska developers and to the good folks at the Pirate Bay.

Please enjoy them !

There will be more coming.. this is simply the beginning.

In return, I ask that you not modify the covers, to ensure they remain dedicated as intended.  :)



Secondary Objective:
Cover sites that demand money should not remain in business, why pay for something you can get for free !


CK
